'''阿拉·古勒'''（{{lang-en|Ara Güler}}, {{bd|1928年|8月16日|2018年|10月17日|catIdx=Güler}}）是一位亚美尼亚裔土耳其摄影师。昵称是“伊斯坦布尔之眼”或“伊斯坦布尔摄影师”。<ref>{{cite news|accessdate=18 October 2018|title='Eye of Istanbul' Ara Guler dies at 90|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-45899844|newspaper=BBC News|date=18 October 2018|via=BBC News|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109084757/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-45899844|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="guardian-larson">{{cite web|first1=Vanessa H.|last1=Larson|accessdate=18 October 2018|title=Photography of Ara Güler captures a forgotten Turkey|url=https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2014/feb/04/ara-guler-anatolia-exhibition-photography-turkey|date=4 February 2014|website=The Guardian|archive-date=2021-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421100415/https://www.theguardian.com/artanddesign/2014/feb/04/ara-guler-anatolia-exhibition-photography-turkey|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ag">{{Cite web |url=http://www.araguler.com.tr/ |publisher=Ara Güler |title=Ara Güler Kimdir? |language=tr |accessdate=4 December 2009 |archive-date=2021-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210523034110/http://www.araguler.com.tr/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Kettmann|first=Steve|title=A Photo Show on a Pogrom 50 Years Ago Is Itself Attacked by a Mob|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2005/09/24/arts/extra/24pogr.html?_r=0|accessdate=23 February 2013|newspaper=The New York Times|date=25 September 2005|archive-date=2020-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529200950/https://www.nytimes.com/2005/09/24/arts/extra/a-photo-show-on-a-pogrom-50-years-ago-is-itself-attacked-by-a-mob.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==生平==
1928年出生于[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]的一个[[亚美尼亚|亚美尼亚]][[基督教|基督教]]移民家庭，父亲经营一家药店。毕业于[[伊斯坦布尔大学|伊斯坦布尔大学]]经济系。之后开启摄影生涯，1961年加入[[馬格蘭攝影通訊社|馬格蘭攝影通訊社]]，和2006年[[诺贝尔文学奖|诺贝尔文学奖]]得主[[奥尔汗·帕穆克|奥尔汗·帕穆克]]是好友，2018年10月17日在[[伊斯坦布尔|伊斯坦布尔]]逝世，享年90岁。<ref name="dailysabah">{{cite news|accessdate=18 October 2018|title=Legendary Turkish photographer Ara Güler loses battle for life at 90|url=https://www.dailysabah.com/turkey/2018/10/17/legendary-turkish-photographer-ara-guler-loses-battle-for-life-at-90|newspaper=[[Daily_Sabah|Daily Sabah]]|archive-date=2018-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181018122306/https://www.dailysabah.com/turkey/2018/10/17/legendary-turkish-photographer-ara-guler-loses-battle-for-life-at-90|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[https://www.sohu.com/a/270118291_114988 帕慕克最爱的摄影师阿拉·古勒去世，生前被誉为“伊斯坦布尔之眼”]，搜狐新闻。</ref>

